js.object.deepize.description:
This function simply take an object like this one:
{
'something.cool': 'hello'
}
and convert it to something like this:
{
something: {
cool: 'hello'
}
}

js.value.typeDefinitionArrayObjectToStri.description:
This function take as parameter a type definition object like this one:
{
type: [{
type: 'Array',
of: [{
type: 'Boolean'
}]
}]
}
an transform it to a string like so "Array<Boolean>"

scss.core.string.function.replace-tokens.description:
Search and replace tokens like colors #primary in a passed string, list or map
Supported tokens types :
1. Colors : #{colorName}

scss.core.color.color-var.description:
Get a registered color by name or wrap a new color into a sugar.color call
to manipulate it with ease.
Supported modifier :
- hue {Deg}
- lighten {Percent}
- darken {Percent}
- saturate {Percent}
- desaturate {Percent}
- grayscale {Boolean}
- complement {Boolean}
- invert {Boolean}
- opacity {Percent}
- mix {Color}
- lightness {Percent}
- saturation {Percent}

